# MTG (Mind The Gap) Attention Vision Transformer — Complete Deep Dive

> This document focuses on what's **unique** to the MTG code. For fundamentals (Q/K/V, softmax, multi-head attention, ViT patch embedding, [CLS] token, positional embeddings, residual connections, LayerNorm, FFN, stable rank, SVD, AdamW, cross-entropy), refer to the [Differential Transformer Deep Dive](file:///Users/simran/.gemini/antigravity/brain/8684e7c8-adf3-4a3c-b05b-1017d40e5a63/differential_transformer_deep_dive.md).

